{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6ed917f09b","title":"中共中央书记处关于七届三中全会的决定","origin":"根据中央文件原件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f41958e0df","index":0,"year":1950,"month":6,"day":4,"articleId":"6ed917f09b"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"a2f6c6af57","name":"陈云","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7741d23a65","type":"title","text":"中共中央书记处关于七届三中全会的决定","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"da1b2fa8b6","type":"paragraph","text":"一、三中全会主席团，提议由书记处同志担任。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"f788845fc1","type":"paragraph","text":"即：毛主席、刘少奇、朱德、周恩来、陈云。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"e18998d277","type":"paragraph","text":"二、全会议事日程：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"40bcf8a3ec","type":"paragraph","text":"1、毛主席报告。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"fea6c8cb84","type":"paragraph","text":"2、刘少奇同志关于土地改革问题的报告。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"e30b63c8a2","type":"paragraph","text":"3、陈云同志关于财政经济问题的报告。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"377410931e","type":"paragraph","text":"4、周恩来同志关于外交和统一战线工作的报告。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"6280dfb07a","type":"paragraph","text":"5、聂荣臻同志关于解放军整编问题的报告。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"b655475b4e","type":"paragraph","text":"以上各报告，均各定为一个钟头。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"7ce2a52adc","type":"paragraph","text":"各同志发言时间，各大行政区主要负责人及指定的专题发言人（计有：高岗、饶漱石、邓子恢、叶剑英、刘伯承、彭德怀、薄一波（税收问题发言）、安子文、乔木[1]等九人，华北一人），每人半个钟头。其余同志发言以十五分钟为限。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"fb79f27037","type":"paragraph","text":"三、全会时间，预定由六月六日起至六月九日止，共四天，每天由下午五时起，十时止，共开五个钟头。休息半小时。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"0293da3233","type":"paragraph","text":"四、决定由少奇、德怀、仲勋、王震、伯承、子恢、克诚、漱石、剑英、彭真、刘澜涛等组成土改问题委员会。由少奇负责。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"8db8f0538b","type":"paragraph","text":"五、任弼时同志因健康尚未恢复，决定不出席全会。在主席报告时，可到会听主席报告。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"c50c4aef30","type":"paragraph","text":"六、决定刘子久同志不出席三中全会报告。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"},{"id":"675b27a9a6","type":"paragraph","text":"批准陈云在任弼时休假期内参加书记处。原政治局决定为候补书记。陈潭秋出缺由黄克诚递补。正式委员七人未到会，照例由候补委员七人补足表决权四十四人。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b"}],"page":{"id":"2e4b359348","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6ed917f09b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}